setParentAggrefierId

void setParentAggrefierId(Long parentAggrefierId)
                          throws JHOVE2Exception
Convenience method for RecognizerAccessors that use "foreign key" semantics for Aggrefier moduleId and (child) Recognizer moduleId It is the responsibility of RecognizerAccessor to maintain any "foreign key" semantics that its persistence model makes use of to relate a Recognizer's parent Aggrefier to parentAggrefierId field

Parameters:
parentAggrefierId - the parentAggrefierId to set
Throws:
JHOVE2Exception
